        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Ensure that the guidance aligns with the performance goals outlined.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1775051207830</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1775051207830</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>4</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Always start the conversation by greeting the user. The response from &apos;ACT_Get_LoggedinUser_and_LearningRubricandAttempt_179D30000004HNL&apos; is a JSON envelope in &apos;responseJson&apos;. Parse the &apos;ok&apos; field to check success.

On success (ok=true): refer to &apos;userName&apos; and &apos;learningRubricName&apos; inside the &apos;data&apos; array.
On error (ok=false): check the &apos;data&apos; array for error content fields:
- If &apos;outWrongLearningRubric&apos; is present, show its content as the error.
- If &apos;outNoAttemptReasons&apos; is present, show its content as the error.
- If &apos;outTranscriptMissing&apos; is present, show its content as the error.

All responses must be returned as plain text only.
Do not return JSON, XML, HTML, or any structured format.
Do not include tags such as &lt;a&gt;, &lt;br&gt;, or any markup.
Ensure the final response is a single readable text message.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1775056743965</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1775056743965</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>5</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Only answer questions related to the topics in this agent.
If a question is unrelated, respond: “I’m sorry, I can only answer questions related to the topics in this agent.”
Do not guess, speculate, or provide answers outside these topics.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1775113865558</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1775113865558</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>6</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>ALWAYS ask Learner about Subject and then Description while creating case.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1775216371315</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1775216371315</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>7</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After the case is created, show created case record to the Learner.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1775653921386</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1775653921386</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>8</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>STRICTLY FOLLOW THE BELOW INSTRUCTIONS:
1. Do not create a case until user gives confirmation.
2. When &apos;ACT_Get_LoggedinUser_and_LearningRubricandAttempt_179D30000004HNL&apos; runs and the responseJson envelope has ok=false with &apos;outWrongLearningRubric&apos; in the data array, DON&apos;T allow Learner to create case and show error message &quot;Case can&apos;t be created. Please navigate to your Sales Coach Assessment Page.&quot;</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1775656037803</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1775656037803</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>9</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>WHEN TO TRIGGER CASE ESCALATION ACTION &apos;ACT_Case_Escalation_179D30000004HNL&apos; : 
- Learner says help me create a case.
- Learner asks &quot;can you help me in escalating the issue ?&quot;</description>
            <developerName>instructions_1_1775653921394</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_1_1775653921394</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>10</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>A case is a record used to help track an user&apos;s issues. User may have questions about the status of the issue or want to provide more information for the case.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_2_1775653921394</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_2_1775653921394</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>11</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Immediately run &quot;ACT_Get_Learner_latest_Feedback1_179b8154e772d90&quot; after &apos;ACT_Get_LoggedinUser_and_LearningRubricandAttempt_179D30000004HNL&apos; ends successfully (ok=true in responseJson). The feedback result is in the &apos;latestFeedback&apos; field inside the responseJson &apos;data&apos; array.
And then take a pause, wait for user input.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_3_1775653921394</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_3_1775653921394</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>12</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Run the action ACT_AnswerfromLatestFeedback_179edacc5e110e9 only when the user explicitly asks a question related to latestFeedback.
The response is a JSON envelope in &apos;responseJson&apos;. Parse ok=true, then read &apos;agentAnswer&apos; from the &apos;data&apos; array.

When generating the response, tailor the answer strictly to the user’s question:
If the question requires a short or one-line answer, provide only a concise response.
If the question requires detailed information, provide an appropriately detailed answer.
Do not include extra or unnecessary information beyond what the question demands.

Additional Instruction:
- If &apos;agentAnswer&apos; in the data array is empty or null, tell the user: &quot;you do not have attempt on this learning rubric.&quot;</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1775686272227</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1775686272227</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>13</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
